Class JSerializeReaderImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • exesoft.JSerializeReaderImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JSerializeReader

    public class JSerializeReaderImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements JSerializeReader
    JSerializeReader - Class responsible for the mapping of the object based on the information obtained from object JModel, which in decoding process (method decode) will create a String object, as we can see in the example.
    String to process in JModel :
    java.lang.Osoba{imie(java.lang.String):x;nazwisko(java.lang.String):y;}
